'''Zsajhira berries''' were native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Socorro/Legends|Socorro]]. Its berries were used by [[Ethra Brewery]] to produce a traditional [[Alcohol/Legends|liquor]] called [[raava]]. Zsajhira berries were also used to make [[Zsajhira berry tea]] and [[Zsajhira berry juice]].<ref name="BSS">''[[The Black Sands of Socorro]]''</ref>

